NCTUECE | Speech Communication Lab




























 NCTUECE | Speech Communication Lab.

本實驗室由 張文輝教授 指導。位於國立交通大學光復校區工程四館812A室。
							
Learn about what we do








Here's Our Research Fields.







-----------------------------






-------------------------------






---------------------------------











張文輝(Wen-Whei Chang) 教授
教授簡介：Wen-Whei Chang received the B.S. degree in communication engineering from National Chiao Tung University, Hsinchu, Taiwan, R.O.C., in 1980, and the M.Eng. and Ph.D. degrees in electrical engineering from Texas A & M University, College Station, TX, in 1985 and 1989, respectively.
						Since 1989, he has been a Faculty Member at the Communication Engineering Department of National Chiao Tung University, Taiwan, where he is currently professor. In the summer of 2000, he was on leave at the school of Electrical and Electronic Engineering,Nanyang Technological University, Singapore. 
單位及職稱：國立交通大學電機工程系暨電信工程研究所甲組(通訊、網路及多媒體領域)教授 
研究專長：合併訊源通道編解碼、分散式訊源編碼、生醫訊號處理、語音及音樂訊號處理
連絡電話：03-5712121 ext 31826 
E-Mail：wwchang@cc.nctu.edu.tw 
主要學歷：Texas A&M University Electrical Engineering Ph.D. 1985-1989Texas A&M University Electrical Engineering M.S. 1983-1985National Chiao-Tung University Communication Engineering B.S. 1976-1980 








Fall 2016
互動式音訊處理導論 Introduction to Interactive Audio Processing









